        "TileImage": "$($repository 73f1046e-7c74-42b6-b4a7-7e4dd34f25af).Image",
        "Description": "So 47. We were able to find out the hacker&apos;s location. He&apos;s at the militant headquarters in Colorado where you eliminated Bradley Payne earlier. However, we cannot identify the hacker, it takes a lot of time, which is not available. That&apos;s why you&apos;re going to eliminate all hackers in Colorado. There are only four of them: GREG BARENS, JOSHUA TRUMBO, FINN JACOBS and ISAAC KAY. All four of them may pose a danger to the ICA. Good luck.",
